\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you say grace at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Not as I can recollect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well as far as I can recollect he's always been Labour. So he must have some - some knowledge of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Do you know why he held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well becau
se - at that time the workers were downtrodden wasn't they? You never had a say in it. If you down anything wrong you was taken to court, you was beaten up all that - all that sort of thing. The working man never stood a chance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about your mother, would she take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. But - my mother - in recent years my mother was a - a - a great friend of George Tomas the M - Labour MP.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 That's latterly of course?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes, that's lately.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When you were younger when you were children, do you think she had any political view I don't think so.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You wouldn't know what she thought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, well I - I should think at that time with all us family she didn't have time for nothing only looking after us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Do you remember your father and your mother voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well all I can remember - at that - election day - all the children used to go around with play}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 cards and colours. Yes. Everybody, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Can you tell me about this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well el
ection day - if you - if your parents voted Labour, you went around with the banners and all that sort of thing in hour hundreds. I think all the children that were there used to go around with flags. Placards, everything, right around. Shouting their hea
ds off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would that be just election day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Election day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 All the different parties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Where would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well different places, the same as they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Children and grown ups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well the children wasn't allowed to go, only the grown ups allowed to go in to vote see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I meant in these processions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, only the children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Do you remember them voting, there was an election in 1918, women had the vote then for the first time? Do you remember whether yo
ur mother and father voted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh expect so.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You wouldn't know what party they voted for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well the - I think they've been Labour all their lives.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 In some places at that time men felt that they risked losing their jobs or their houses if
 they voted differently from their employers, do you know if your father ever felt himself under that kind of pressure, to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well, the only thing - the only thing as I found out - since - that the only man they could throw 
out was a man in a - a - a farm labourer. If he packed his job he had to pack his house and get out. Now may father had that experience in Surrey. Yes. My father was - on an estate in Sully. And he packed his job and he had to get out. But in regards of -
 
a man losing his job because he voted - against his - employer, I think that's all rubbish. Because that was asking for trouble wasn't it I don't say - I - I don't say that - the employers - the employer - didn't force his men to whether they vote Labour 
or whatever he was - or whatever he was voting. There was - there was a lot of push behind them. So you got to vote for me or - things look very rough for you, that's how it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You do think it was like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would your father have felt that do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Was your father ever a member of a party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Do you remember him working for one of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about your mother, would she be a member?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did your parents take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well I couldn't say off hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You don't remember when you were a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What did your father do when he came home from work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well if you wanted me to speak candidly? I - I think he spent his time like the same as the rest, in the pub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 My mother - my mother used to stop at home, look after all the family. She didn't have much time to do any other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would she have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well she used to go to the old }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 Coliseum}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 , you know, the first picture house in Canton that was. I don't know about - ah, the whist drive I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would that be before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Before the - yes, before the world war. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 She used to like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would she go regularly, say once a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes, she - her and her friend next door, Mr Crawle, she used to go to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 
Coliseum}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 . I think it was tuppence to go in. And if you had a cup of tea and a bun.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What would be on in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 Coliseum}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734  then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well the old pictures, you know, the old time pictures.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 She'd go with the lady next door?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 That's her friend was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Nobody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
No. Because - me and my two pals went missing from school one day, and we decided to go to the pictures. So when the lights went up after one picture come off, I could see my father 
- my mother and my - her friend in the front. And we had to get underneath the seats hide out the way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did she see you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No she didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When did your father get home from work in the evenings, what time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well all times. I think it - I - well, it's a job to say - an - all hours. All according to where he was working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 He was driving horses wasn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well he used to walk - he was telling me he used to walk from Cardiff to Pontypridd to work - as a timber}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 And walk back then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 And so I don't know whether he'd have a lift back, but he used to walk to - he used to walk to Pontypridd to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How many evenings a week would you think he'd spend at home with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well he couldn't go out very much because - the
y never had the money to go out. The trouble was in them days - as far as I could understand - the bosses - would buy them beer. I know - I know the - I know that for a fact in my own father. I know the firm he worked for. Because I worked with the same f
irm for a couple of months And they tried it on me but I wouldn't wear it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What did they used to do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - I - I - I was working at the quarry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What did they do to buy them beer like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - he would be out working, perhaps 
he'd have a couple of load to take to town. Well - to coax you on a bit they'd take you in the pub and give you a couple of point Well they'd never think of paying you overtime. I - I had that - I had that experience with the same firm but - I stuck it ab
out two months and packed it in.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did your father attend any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 But he would go to the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Go to the pub, I only - there was not many clubs about in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would he go regularly to the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, it wouldn't be every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Just the Friday and Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You don't remember what he used to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would he go a couple of times a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well he - he used to go and there used to be a terrible row when he come home. I do know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes, my - my - my mother used to - play hell with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would he come home drunk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would that be a couple of times a week or just now and again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would your mother go to the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. Not 'til latter end. When my mother - my - my mother was - well on in age she start a glass of beer in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 But when you were children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You don't remember her ever going to a club or a pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did your father take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Boxing. He lived for boxing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did he box himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 He'd go to watch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 He'd live for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Was there any cock fighting about then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would your father go to the boxing often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well I - I - I couldn't say offhand. But lived for boxing. Yes. He used to get the boxing books every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did he ever go to the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes, Ely. I also went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When you were a little boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You'd go with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. Well we lived a couple of - about half a mile from there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How often would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well when - they had only - have - used to have racing there about twice a year. No flat racing, all over the sticks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did your father bet? Would he bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. Only in late years.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Not when you were younger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs? They used to have clubs in those days didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 For buying boots, and a sick club? Do you remember if your father and mother belonged to anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. I don't think so. It might - it might be unknown to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You don't remember somebody going to pay so much a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Or somebody coming to the door?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Your uncle, was he head of the Odd}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 fellows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would your father and mother have belonged to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. Because when my uncle died I had all his - stuff you know. The apron and all the - gear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 All right. We was all right, we was happy family in them days. Of course when you get older you alter a bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When you were children you didn't quarrel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. No. We wasn't - we wasn't allowed to quarrel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Was there one of them that you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 My brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Fred?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Because there were only you two boys weren't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. I practically nursed him. Up 'til the time he got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 But he was a year older than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. He -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You were very close were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. We were very close 'til he started courting. Then he started on this - beer stunt you know, drinking. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 But you were very close when you were boys were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. 'Til time I was up about seventeen. Then we seemed to drift apart.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 As a child who did you play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - chaps like myself, girls, you all mixed up playing together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you play with your brother, your sisters or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - it'd be neighbours you know, boys about their own age, we never bothered with girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You didn't play with your sisters so much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. They had their own interests.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Where did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Out in the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you ever play in somebody else home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well in them days used to - t
hey was all neighbours, but they very rare went into one another's houses. Used to get their old front room - for Sundays, and you wasn't allowed to look in the door. Well you know that. Of course as you got a bit older so you went further a field. But we
 spent biggest part of our time in Ely river. Bathing of a sum - in the summer. Then the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Who would be with you then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh about fifty or sixty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 The boys from the neighbourhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Boys, yes. I was pulled out three times. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You were living near a river weren't you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. Well that's only place that we had in life really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 It was quite suitable for bathing in then was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 It was quite suitable for bathing in then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. The river - the river was clean then, there was no factories.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Do you remember what games you played when you were children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - in school my first game was rugby. Only one game ruby, wasn't allowed to play football.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about the games you played with children in the street and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well there wasn't so much games then, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you play hide and seek?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Ah.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Marbles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Marbles, all them games, we used to - that they seem to play now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You don't remember anything else, any other sort of game you used to play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Football. Football was our - mostly our main sport when we got up - about the age. Well then - same they did on the mountains. We used to up there and - what they call catch 'em a writhing. Aye. I had to - I h
ad to - and if the boss caught you had a sore behind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Wasn't it dangerous?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
No. And they used to bring - the cows - so many cows on Leckworth common, and every so oft - every - twice a day they'd come down on their own, into Canton - into the sta
ble to be milked. Used to come on their own, they had - they'd no need to bring these cows home. Used to belong to Mrs Thomas, in Leckworth Road, used to walk right on the back lanes, over the - over the crossing where the railway used to cross the road. 
Of course they've done away with that crossing. Build that new bridge.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you get milk from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you get milk from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well we wouldn't. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only - only when you were dressed for - after school. But not Sundays. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Your mother didn't mind in the weekdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 But Sunday you had to keep clean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Sunday you had to keep clean. You put your - you put your new suit on Sunday morning - af
ter dinner you took it off. And then put your - then put your other clothes on. Because you had a hell of a job to buy clothes that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Were you free to play with anyone you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Your parents, would they discourage you from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
No, we - we used to knock about - about - the same three families. No, four families. And it's the only four families that - that'd get together. That was a - Mrs Cross's boy, next door, Mrs Moore's boys. And Mrs Hilliard}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 s boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Why was that I wonder?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Because - we simp - we - we - we mixed up as a gang as youngsters, all went to the same school. And we always stuck}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You formed a gang did you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well it used to be little gangs in them days. And t
hey didn't throw stones and - and - and - and - hit you with chains. You had to settle your difference with your fists on the common.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Were you called anything, did you have a name for the gang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. Shorty, that's all I used to hear. Shorty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only - the Salvation Army Life Saving Scouts. That was a - bringing you up to - to service. Life Saving.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Life saving on the beach?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you used to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I should like to as
k you about how you spent your free time when you were at school. Did you have any hobbies, what would you do in your spare time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 We had to walk - it's close on three mile to school. Twelve o'clock you had three miles to walk back. You had three mile
s to go to school again. At half past four you had three mile to walk back, so you didn't have no spare time to do nothing. You - you only had one hobby. And you was compelled to do that in school, was a half an hour's Welsh every day. Yes. Learn to speak
 Welsh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You had a Welsh lesson at school then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would they give you work to do at home you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you keep any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Pigeons. YES. My father kept a - the fowls out the back, and I kept the racing pigeon loft on top. I used to race them. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What was that like?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Well it was - pretty expensive. Not like it is today. And they used to pay for theirselves, we used to win a few races. From up around Newcastle way and all that way. And I used to spend biggest part of my time with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 It would take quite a lot of your time wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. I used to spend a lot of time with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you say you had rabbits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. I used to let them run the back. Breed in the back. They used to dig down i
n the - garden, and breed there. Of course they couldn't go over the next back because the - stones was so far down, they couldn't get under the next back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You were breeding those for food weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you collect anything, boys used to collect birds eggs and cigarette cards an things like that didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well all I can remember about them is the silk - the silk cards, the silk cards and the - BDV cigarettes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you collect those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I - I did start collect them. They were like in a silk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Flower patterns on silk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. Make 'em up to a picture.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you do any gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You didn't have any other kind of hobbies like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, we - we didn't have no garden nor nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You wouldn't collect stamps or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you go fishing?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Not in the river?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, I had no patience for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you go for walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Plenty of walk. Used to think nothing of walking to Barry Island of a Sun
day. Walking back. We used to do all our - lot of running up around on Leckworth Woods. Climbing trees and all that sort of thing, as youngsters, as you would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you spend a lot of time out of doors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. Biggest part of our time was out of doors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What would you do when it was raining?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Stop in the house I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you go bicycling at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Never had a bike.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only football. Football and rugby, that's all you had in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you go to any theatres?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
I always remember when I was a youngster - was going to the - Palace, in Wescott Street. That's the first time I ever remember my father taking me there. And they used to have a little bioscopes. That's when they co
me out I suppose as far as I know, that's when the pictures come out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you ever go to a concert?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
No. The only - the only place you'd go to - was these lantern things in the - Memorial Hall. And the Salvation Army, slides you know. Used to get plenty of custom there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 They'd run an evening for you would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. About once a week.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would there be any music halls, would you go to any music halls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Cinemas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only once ever I went to a cinema. I think it was a
bout 1911 - when Captain Scott went to the Pole. And when he came back we seen the pictures, we was taken free from school to see these pictures. And that was in - that was in the old Penoptican. In St Mary Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You remember going from school, a party of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh dear. All as I could remember - we used to get a ha'penny every Saturday. That was - that was your pocket money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you have it every week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Wel
l - it's been the same all the world over. Everybody got their favourites. Don't matter what line it's in. Some children can't do wro - do no wrong, and some will do it all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Were there gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Groups just the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Any gangs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes, used to be Greenstone and Canton. There was always trouble when Greenstone and Canton met, especially after school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Were there any children who were left out of things? Weren't accepted into a gang
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, I can't - I can't say that there was. Were all about the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you go on to another school after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Hold old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I should think I was just over thirteen and a half.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. We had one ambition then, to get out and earn some money. That was every boy's ambition.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you attend any part time education afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. I don't think - I don't think there was any places for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 None at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 Do you think you benefi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 ted from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well I've learnt - a lot more since I've been out of school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Do you thin}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 k you benefi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 ted at all from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well it was - I
 think it was a case - that you had to go to school. There was a go many didn't want to go but we had to go. And you had to - to - learn what they taught you. You done it the best of your ability, you couldn't do no more. They was teaching me Welsh, I cou
l
dn't grasp Welsh no more than the man in the moon. So it was a waste of time wasn't it? My interest wasn't in that. You can't learn in half an hour to speak Welsh. Or half an hour every week. It - I think it's the hardest language there is to pick up. I w
as good - I - there was only one thing I was - backward on, that was writing. As far as - figure work I was all right. And I could do it better now than I ever done it in my life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 While you were at school did you have a part time job, or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. I was a - a milkman in the mornings as I told you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You did two jobs didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You had the milk}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Milk}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
round in the morning. And lather boy at night.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 And you were an errand boy in the ironmongery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Ah, I used to - I used to do that Saturdays, only one day, Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about the milk}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 round, how did you get that job, how did you hear about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well the man was living close handy to us. And I used to have a litt
le truck, and the - and the - the milk tins, there was no jugs and bottles, used to have the tins. Well the - every customer used to have a certain tin, with a cover on, and you'd know what house to take it to. Take the truck back. And then go home and ge
t ready for school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What time did you have to start?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 About six in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 For how long did you do it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 About an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Every day of the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Every day - well, I - I don't think I used to go Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You used to go Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, Saturdays. I remember the milk man, I knew where - I could take you to his house now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How much did he pay you for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh I couldn't - oh it's so long ago I forget. It wasn't a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No idea how much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Do you remember whether you felt then it was a fair wage you were having for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - at them times you - you didn't realize the value of money. If he was catching you he - he knew more about it than what you did.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How long did you do it for, how many months or years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I don't think I done it very long. Too early in the morning.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What was it spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh helping towards the household.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get on with the milkman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 All right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Was it only just you and him or were there other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You got on all right with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did he treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - pretty good, pretty decent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 As far as I could recollect the man was all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you feel about the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - the work is - the work was all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 But I didn't mind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did it alter your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well no, as I said before, I - I didn't care for school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 The other job you did then was a lather boy?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well that I couldn't say, but I remember the barber. I remember the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Lather. Lather a man and rub the lather in before the barber shaved him. And sometimes used to be twelve o'clock before I got home Saturday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What time did you have to start in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 About dinnertime. 
Only on a Saturday, not on the night - on the weeknights, only Saturday. Of course that was a busy time for the barbers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What did they pay you for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Half a crown I believe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you get any tips as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. Might get a clip in the ear}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 hole if you - if you was to do something wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 From the barber or a customer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 The barber.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you feel it was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well at that time yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you give that to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What would it be spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 The same, help towards the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get on with the people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 All right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 The barber?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Always have been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did the barber treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well the same as anybody else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 All right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What did you feel about it, what did you feel about him, about the barber?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well he's the same as any other man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
feel about the work, did you like it or did you dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I - I never - I never disliked work. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 The only other part time job you had was in the ironmonger wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Aye, I used to go errand boys sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 That was after you finished the lathering?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How long did you do the lathering job for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Not long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Few months or a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I was there long enough to use a - a razor. Open razor. He tea - he taught me to us an open razor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 So you progressed from just being a lather lad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You progressed to shaving did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, I never shaved nobody. But he taught me how to use a razor. I can use a razor on anybody. I've shaved my brother many a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How long do you think how were there, a couple of years probably?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. You're not there no time but they're teaching you the trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about this errand boy job, you were doing that while you were in school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes, Slight - Slight's the ironmongers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get hold of that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well through - they used to advertise in the window. Put a - paper in the window, errand boy wanted for today or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Well go take the - small orders to people's houses. Say you went to order - anything in the shop - you'd have it sent. Well they'd have errand - errand boys to do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you have to walk then with it or go on a bike?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Walk, or on a bike.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You'd use a bike there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I think they had a bike, I'm not certain.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well they used to shut early them days. The big shops in Canton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 It was only a Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What time would you go in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
About nine. Sweep - sweep the shop out. Sweep the shop, do the floors, everything tidy. Then you'd go back in the shop mo - mucking round 'til there was an order to take out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When would you finish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 About six. When the shop shut.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What were you paid for that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Five shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you feel that was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 It was a good wage at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I should run home as fast as I could and give it to her. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What was it spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Household, everything was for the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get on with the people there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 All right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Well he - you - you didn't have to feel about any - any - anybody then - in them times. You - they spoke as ordinary - man would do. I got on all right with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you feel about the work, did you like it or did you dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - it was - it was bringing a few shillings in so you - you took the rough with the smooth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I'd like to ask you about your first full time job. When you left school what did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When I left school - I put m
y age on and started in a paper mill. Ely paper mill. From six in the morning 'til six at night. For seven and six a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you work Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Saturday seven - six days a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 So no half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh applied to the mill for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Shave - what they call a shaving boy. When they made these big reels of paper - used to have to cut the - shave the ends off. They used to go through a machine. And perhaps they'
d take that much off each end they cut the per - paper perfect. Well all that used to go in a pit. Well you used to have to get - get it out of the pit then they'd take it to the beaters to be made up as paper again, into pulp. I wasn't there very long.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
About a couple of months. I went to the manager and asked him for a rise. He give me a rise. The following week I went up for another one. 'Til I ran - 'til I was highest boy paid boy in the - paper mill, I had fourteen and seven}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 pence a week
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What did you start at?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Seven and six. So - when the war broke out - I packed the job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You packed it in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 Yes. And I was pass}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
ing a yard in Leckworth Road, and I seen this man there with these big horses and I asked him for a job. 
He said, you know anything about horses? I said, I know a bit. All right, he says, go in there and saddle that horse, put the harness on him. And he was a - and he was a big horse too. I eventually saddled the horse, put him - in the - in the - trolley as
 
they call - as they called 'em than, and he put me to work hauling bricks from Brickyard Road in - St Well to Victoria Park. Of course there were no houses in Victoria Park then. So when I come home at night, in the - for to pull in the yard my father was
 there. And my father was head man for this - for this firm. When I went in he asked me who started me. Driver, yes. So from there we went up - went up the other side of Bargoed. Timber falling. I was lodging in Pontlodin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 While you were in the Ely paper mills you were telling me you were paid seven and six to start with, did you feel it was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You asked for two rises?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you think the fo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 u}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 rteen and seven was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Every ha'penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What was it spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh the same thing, the household.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get on with the people in the paper mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 All right. Of course they was all boys and - grown men on the machines.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Who was your employer there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Paper mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did they treat you, how did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well they didn't worry you - how they treated you as long as they had the work done. That's all that concerned them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you feel about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well you had no option but to go to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you like the work or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh you had to like it, don't matter whether - you had to do it whether you liked it or no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Then you went on to driving the horses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What hours did you work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - we went up to - Bargoed - we had three hundred acres of timber up there to mow f}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 rom}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 . Used to get up at six in the morning - and get home at six at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you have to work on Saturday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only Saturday mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
We used to come home Sundays. My father come home one Sunday, and I'd stop there look after the horses and that. Then the following week I'd come home and he'd stop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You were staying up in Bargoed were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, we - we was - lodging in Pontlodin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Was it only you and your father or were there other men?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only me and my father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What were you paid now for driving the horses? This would have been in the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. The war - the war had started. I don't suppose I was getting two pound a we
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you feel it was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, not for the work I was doing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 All of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about your lodgings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
My father paid that. Yes. We used to buy our own food. All we used to get was a bed and - what they called bed and vegetables. Used to pay three and six a week for that. For the bedroom, bed and vegetables. So -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 It was in a caf\'e9 or something you were staying?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 We - when we went there first we was in a cafe. But we didn't stop there long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You went into a house then did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would they make the food for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 But you'd buy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 It was only your father you were working with was it, you didn't work with anybody else up there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes, we had - what they called timber}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244156\charrsid1851734 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 men, that was the men at their trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 They were felling the trees?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 And you were carting it away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get on with the other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 All right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Champion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you like the work or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well I - I liked the life, it was a good life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How long did you do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 'Til 1917.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What happened then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Then - we finished the contracts. So - I asked the boss for more money, I wasn't getting a fair deal. I was getting the same money for driving one wagon as I was for driving three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How much was that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
The same money, two pound a week. So I couldn't get no more money so I packed it in. So I had to walk around and I started on the Cardiff Water Works.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh - I was looking for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you see it advertised?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. You - you went around on your bike and - went to different places, different firms and work was very scarce then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 During the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What exactly did you have to do in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 On the filter beds. T
aking out the filter beds and washing everything and putting in all back, of course there was - seven or eight men in a gang then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What hours did you wok there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Ordinary hours. Working hours, seven - seven 'til five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you work Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only on overtime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would that be often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only when the ice - when the weather was bad you had ice on the filters, because the had to be broken - taken out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 So it was a five day week was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Five - six day week. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you have a half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only Saturdays.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You worked seven 'til five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 And seven 'til when on Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Seven 'til twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you have holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What were you paid there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I think after the health insurance and one thing and another you drew about - two pound twelve and - tuppence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you feel it was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well the - all the county seemed to thing it was a fair wage. The council - the coun
cil and all of them, they thought it was a fair wage. You had - you had no option of what you thought.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What did you feel though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You either done it or - you starved. That - that was the end of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you feel it was a fair wage though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well I never - I never thought a working man had a fair wage. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you give any of that money then to your mother
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I used to give my mother half a crown a week. That was after I was married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 This was still before you were married wh
en you started in the water works wasn't it When you first went to work in the water works did you keep your money then and just pay your mother two and six?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, I used to give mother my money. Yes. Yes, 'til I got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You were still in the water works when you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. YES?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get on with the people in the water works, the other people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Lovely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Like one of his own really. Well all of us, we was all classed the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You liked it there, you liked the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. If you was a good workman you could get on with any of 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How long were you doing that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well I got transferred to another department on the water works. On what they called a servicing department.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh I'd say a couple - a few years after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 After the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 After you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 After - after we was married and after the war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You were married in 1922 weren't you, so how long were you working in the water works altogether?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Twenty-eight years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 That's the only job you had then was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You haven't had another job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When did you finish with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When did I finish, 1950 or 51. No. What are you talking about, 1950 when I finished on the water works, my health -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You went to the army in 1939?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 And you were there for four years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Close on four years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Then you came out, you went back to the water works did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. No. I came out and I went on the buildings for two years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You were finished with the water works before you went to the army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 After I come out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You did go back to them for a short while?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, I - I'd finished when I come out. I never went back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You went on the building?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What were you doing there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Laying the footings, foundations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Asking for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Not in the Employment Exchange?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. I
 done it about two years and I went back on the water - they kept on at me to go back in the water works as a jointer, a lead jointer. I went back and I think it was 1950 I finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 So you were in the building trade from about 1945?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 To about 1947?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 And then you went back to the water works?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Water works, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Until 1950?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Quite right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 And then you had to finish for ill health?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you have preferred another type of job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, I've been well satisfied.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you have to serve an apprenticeship or training period for any of your jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you belong to a trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you take part in any of its activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. My life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You've been a trade union man all your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. Some years ago we had a bit of trouble. Well this trouble was going on a long time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 When you were in the water works?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. So this particular morning we called a general strike. It didn't last long, onl
y about hour and a half. He wanted us - we used to go out every morning and get wringing wet. No covers, had nothing - no cover to keep us dry, we refused to go out So they threatened to sack us all so I said, we'll - all right, we'll call a general strik
e and walk out. At nine o'clock it was all thrashed out. We beat the - we beat the water works.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Were you an official in the trade union?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. My mate was. My mate was shop steward. So he asked me, he said, what's the best thing to do. I said, wel
l it's to call a strike. There's only one way you're going to settle it, you won't get no - nothing better with what we don't. And they wouldn't give me the sack. Because I'm not boasting or bragging, I could - I could - I knew - I knew a damned sight mor
e
 than any inspectors on the job knew. Because when I went back the second time - they were asking me to find things that they couldn't find. And water mains was being - mislaid and one thing and another. They'd look years for them and I could go straight 
o
ut and find these things for 'em. I never exaggerate because I was always - they thought the world of me there. There's any job, any overtime, all right Ivor, I don't mind mate. My mate's name was Long, Frank Long. It used to be the Long and Short of it, 
he's about six foot six. He lived just by here. He dropped dead.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Any other trade union activities you took part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. We had no need to then. There were a seaman's - there was a seaman's - riot down the docks, and I suppose the Chinese were bro
ught into it. So - all the rioting went on and they smashed every Chinese shop in Cardiff. And I remember the one on the corner of the street I was living, where they - where they - throw - smashed all the windows, threw all their clothes out, it didn't m
a
tter whose clothes it was, they was all thrown out in the street. Of course the first one there had a shirt, or anything that was going. And they set fire to the - to the shops. And then there was a - the trouble with the blacks down there. The Arabs and 
t
he - ordinary Africans, that was another riot. I can remember them getting shot through the - old Theatre Royal. Tom - a chap by the name of Tom Barry used to live at the Echoes. And I think again, if my memory serves me right, there was a - there was a c
rowd used to call themselves the Angry Marches. And they went up on Leckworth Common on this Sunday to dig it all up, claim the ground. And I think they had all the Cardiff police there to shift 'em off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you feel that the employers and workers had the same interests or different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Well I don't think the employers then had the interest in the working man. All he was concerned about was what he could get out of a working man. And I found that out as - I found that out with a good many years after when I was working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Did you feel that there were divisions of interest among workers, some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers? Did you feel that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Of course there was that class distinction. You get it today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about then, years ago, before the war, did you feel that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, because I never worked with 'em. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 They were always unskilled workers really, you were working with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well we were skilled workers but we never mixed with them people. You had to be a skilled man to use an axe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 So you didn't work with labourers really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, no. Of course timber falling was a skilled trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you have to serve an apprenticeship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Or a training period?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. What - what I - what I know my father taught me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well it's bound to. When you - when you was a child you didn't worry so much did you you did
n't have that - them thoughts. And when you - when you reached the age of going to work well you had to do it all - or starve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about your life at home after you left school, did you continue to live at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You were away in Pontlodin in lodgings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I was away - I was away for about - three years in lodgings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 But you were coming home every other weekend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Every fortnight. Only - only for a Sunday, back again the Sunday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You didn't sleep Saturday night at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Yes, come home - come home on the Saturday and go back Sunday night on the - what they used to call the - on the old workman's, on the - on the railway, all the miners used to go up on that train.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well I couldn't say, but I always thought the world of my parents. And always have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you spend Sunday any differently then when you were working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Well we was feeling our feet a bit then. I don't say drinking ever - I never had a glass of beer 'til I was eighteen. I never smoked one of them 'til I was eighteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 So that was after 1918? Did you spend you Sunday differently, did you go to church in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Not after - no, no - I never went to church then - not 'til I was in the army.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Not until you were in the army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 1939?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well that's a funny thing to say. All - this last few years I have been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 But not in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I'm talking now about up to 1918.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What would you do in the evenings, the spare time you had now when you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well, go to the pictures or s
omething like that. Go down the billiard hall, have a game of billiards. I was the champion in my time. That was in the area, area champion. Because I won a cue and case, off \endash  Inn-man. He put up a cue and case. For the best man in the club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What club would that be?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 In the YM.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You used to go the YM when you started working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Before the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Would you go every night or a few times a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well perhaps go in every night, call in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Go on your own, go with your friend, anybody. There was always someone there, there was always friends in the YM.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you make any new friends now when you started work, you had all your pals from the houses around you didn't you when you were in school?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
No, I - myself - I was always a loner. YES. I had friends, but I'd sooner be - how can you say - I didn't mix very well after I started work. I had - either used to go to the pictures. Go down the billiard hall, have a couple of game
s of billiards or - dominoes, whatever they got going there, there was a rifle range there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You'd go on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. Well I on only had to go down the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you make any new friends at all, or girlfriends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes, I had a girl friend down Grangetown. No, not her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 How did you meet her, how did you meet your new friends then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Through my sister. They were working in the laundry together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you ever take your friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No. I wasn't that serious. Still my - my parents knew her, every body knew her like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you have any special friends at this time?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Only one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 This one girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I used to go down and see her - two or three times a week. But something cropped up and we parted and that was that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Where would you go with her, would you go to her home or would you take her out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Oh only on the corner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 The first one I took home was the missus.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did your parents expect to know where you were when you went out in the evening after you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. And I had to be home by ten o'clock. Yes. On the dot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did they meet your friends, if you made new friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No, you never used to take them home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 And you had to be in by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. Ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What would happen if you didn't come in by ten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well you had a thick ear hole.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 After you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes. And since I've been married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you take an interest in politics at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Not at that time, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you have any views at all then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
Yes. I always believe - and always - have believed, the only time a working man comes in this country, is when he can carry a rifle. And I've proved it for years. Because a working m
an is ne - never recognised in this country unless there's a war. Is that right or wrong?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you feel that then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 I felt it all - I've felt it - not before the first world war because I didn't think nothing about war. Only what I'd read in scho
ol about the years gone by.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 What about in the 1914/18 war, you were working then, what did you think about things then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well the same as I - the same as everybody else thought.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You didn't have the vote then did you, you weren't old enough, but what would you have voted if you could have, what party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well you - well - if I was interested in politics at the time it'd have been the Labour party.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You weren't a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Well - were - really we was member of th
e Labour party because we was paying the union. We was paying so much a week towards the party, same as they are today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you ever work for - there was an election 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Did you ever work in the election time for the Labour Party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Nothing like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 You didn't take part in any political activity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 
No, the only one that took any part - in a - politics is my - sister in Canton, she was the chairman of the Labour Party, and my other sister was chairman of the Conservatives in Grangetown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid608221 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 That was after the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15285327 IS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16059240\charrsid1851734 Yes.
\par }}